He says &quot;people are right to fear being replaced&quot;, and we need international coordination on AI.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656848716_17955146232088635_8293469661545529282_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDA0MTk5NzY0OTc5OTY2NDE3OTU1MTQ2MjI5MDg4NjM1.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=AYG_Ci8jqXYQ7kNvwE3LYfb&amp;_nc_oc=AdrqooSzNZIFiKTEJ_cF7DTslZT6e2r3YQH6ndr_edj09pORJ5-buQWmtEMULU5zO5Q&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=CC0bpFXXkW6DDSGtOt12gg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afyaqes0-K7-Sjt941PiKzTxO0GR2qymY18OASiooybDSw&amp;oe=69C8D325" alt="Instagram billede fra @ai_ctrl" /></p><p><strong>@ai_ctrl</strong></p><p>University of Toronto Professor David Duvenaud, who led AI safety testing at Anthropic, tells Canadian MPs that teaching is becoming depressing as students see their skills devalue.<br/>
<br/>
He says &quot;people are right to fear being replaced&quot;, and we need international coordination on AI.</p>]]></content:encoded>
