      <title>MIT professor and AI researcher Max Tegmark says if we fail to regulate AI and b...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWRGtnsgSMw/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656114786_17955108450088635_625506456833936787_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTg5NTg3ODkxMTMzNzI2NDE3OTU1MTA4NDQ3MDg4NjM1.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=9umks9vuM8YQ7kNvwGquZQ8&amp;_nc_oc=AdrLnqK7owah0kwOCxNTUs7779v1CRe1IMmwMxgKhlLDRWCvbZgRFRfWmM9s5rQrnyY&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=CC0bpFXXkW6DDSGtOt12gg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzY_SLC9EyI3RLPFJ1i9y_4y6spdmzw_Fldxx4VCdApOg&amp;oe=69C8C440" alt="Instagram billede fra @ai_ctrl" /></p><p><strong>@ai_ctrl</strong></p><p>MIT professor and AI researcher Max Tegmark says if we fail to regulate AI and build superintelligence it&#x27;s pretty clearly going to be &quot;game over&quot; for humanity. He says it&#x27;s like falling into the Niagara River upstream from the waterfall, that&#x27;s when you lose control.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656114786_17955108450088635_625506456833936787_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTg5NTg3ODkxMTMzNzI2NDE3OTU1MTA4NDQ3MDg4NjM1.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=9umks9vuM8YQ7kNvwGquZQ8&amp;_nc_oc=AdrLnqK7owah0kwOCxNTUs7779v1CRe1IMmwMxgKhlLDRWCvbZgRFRfWmM9s5rQrnyY&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=CC0bpFXXkW6DDSGtOt12gg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzY_SLC9EyI3RLPFJ1i9y_4y6spdmzw_Fldxx4VCdApOg&amp;oe=69C8C440" alt="Instagram billede fra @ai_ctrl" /></p><p><strong>@ai_ctrl</strong></p><p>MIT professor and AI researcher Max Tegmark says if we fail to regulate AI and build superintelligence it&#x27;s pretty clearly going to be &quot;game over&quot; for humanity. He says it&#x27;s like falling into the Niagara River upstream from the waterfall, that&#x27;s when you lose control.</p>]]></content:encoded>
